⌚Compatible Devices and Long Battery Life: Our smartwatches are compatible with IOS 10.0 and above, Android 5.0 and above or above smartphones. Equipped with 260mAh high-capacity battery, magnetic charging, charging time is about 2 hours, it can be used for up to 5-7 days after full charge, and standby for about 15 days.

When your smartwatch is connected to your mobile APP, the weather information will be automatically synced to your device. You can check the weather for the day on your smartwatch and better plan your day. The watch can display weather conditions for 7 days.

Sports Assistant Outdoor Running/Outdoor Walking/Climbing/Outdoor Cycling/Badminton/Table Tennis/Basketball/Skipping Rope/Yoga/Exercise Record This stylish smartwatch can help you time your workouts and improve your workouts. to maximize your exercise efficiency

How to connect a smartphone? 1. Turn on the bluetooth of the mobile phone, scan the APP "Fundo Health" on the manual, download the APP, open the APP, and find the device 2. Look for the device "QW33", the phone pops up to allow "QW33" to display "iPhone" notifications, click Allow, and the notifications of your mobile device will be synchronized to the watch. (Take an Apple phone as an example) How does the watch show notifications? When you connect the mobile phone, the mobile phone will display whether to allow the "QW33" to display the "iPhone" notification, click Allow to open the message notification of the mobile app, and you can select the software you want to display the information. How does the watch connect to a Bluetooth call? 1. The watch needs to be connected to two bluetooths, the first one is "QW33", we need to connect when we are looking for a device 2. The second is "call watch", the gesture slides down to bring up the drop-down menu, click the icon in the lower left corner (equivalent to turning on the Bluetooth switch on the watch), then turn on the Bluetooth of the mobile phone, look for "call watch", and click pairing, at this time The watch will show that the pairing is successful, and you can make a Bluetooth call. (See the manual for details)

NOTE A pop-up window will pop up after logging in to the APP, please always allow the APP to access the mobile phone to send and view information, device location information, address book, make calls and manage calls, call records, device information, and other permissions.During the connection process of mobile phone Bluetooth, the mobile phone will pop up a Bluetooth pairing request, please select to allow pairing.Smartwatch data cannot be used for medical purposes. The monitoring data is for reference only. If you need medical help, please contact a medical professional.Due to the problem of logistics and transportation time, please fully charge the watch for about 2 hours when you get the watch to ensure the normal use of the battery.

reviews.reviewText: It's sleek, easy to pair, lots of fitness features, overall great buy and affordable. Enjoy.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 31, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars A Great Value for the Money
reviews.reviewText: I received the smart watch in just 2 days and it looks great and was very easy to set up after scanning the bar code included on the watch. The only problem I encountered was the clasp on the metal band. I reached out to the manufacture and explained the clasp didn't work to my satisfaction. They responded immediately with an apology. They explained they don't exchange just a band, but in the interest of good customer service, they could offer me a $15.00 refund so I could have the band repaired or buy a new one. That seemed fair to me and I accepted their kind offer. Credit was applied to my account, and I'll be ordering a new band. I must say I am very happy with the customer service I received from the FILIEKEU company. The watch looks great and so far has worked to my expectations. I'm happy to recommend this company to anyone.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 3, 2024
Reviewed in the United States on February 24, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I’ll start off by saying it’s obviously only 50$ you can’t expect much. Learned early in life you get what you pay for, however I would have given the watch a better rating had it been made out of better material upon removing it from the package you can tell it is made extremely cheap. Just by shaking it lightly I can tell and hear how cheap it is. I don’t expect the watch to last me any longer than 4 months I originally only got it to read my blood pressure which it seems to do rather accurately, aside from it being made cheap the watch does operate nicely and setup was rather easy. It does come with a tool to remove links if you need to which is nice I didn’t expect that. To summarize made cheap but operates as expected just don’t expect it to last long if you have an active day to day life.
